                    <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Topicgroup16.png" id="image_kw2_hqn_zjb"
                        />Insert Topic Group</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>Opens the <xref href="dita-insert-topic-ref.dita#dita-insert-topic-ref"
